questions.quote: You know what? You know what? If, things were the other way around, there's nothing you could put on a list that would ever make me not want to be with you.
Fine, she can stay at my place. By the way, what-what does Cassie even look like now.
Okay, but there is a wire back there! I mean that switch is connected to something!
Agh, what a jerk. I kept talking about you and he kept asking me out. I mean, naturally, you know, I said no.
You know, the strippers, and the guys dancing, and you know, pee-pee's flying about.
Excellent! Excellent, now-now do you want another question or a Wicked Wango card?
Hmm, care to make it interesting? I'll bet you that she'll have it by this time tomorrow.
Last night was wonderful. But I-I can't stay here just for you.
This is Monica! I'm Phoebe's friend. Listen, Phoebe is back with David and he's going to propose to her, and she is going to say "yes" but I know she really wants to be with you!
Really? Weird. Anyway, see, I planned everything really well. I planned and I planned and I planned. It just turns out, I don't think I planned enough time to actually do it.
